captions.text: - Ah, I'm a lady reading a book.
Ah, this is how I walk.

- Ah, I have my ba, ba, baby.
- This is how you sound, ah.
- Stop, you wouldn't like to be tickled.
- Oh, baby doesn't like to be tickled.
- Did you child lock the windows?
- Stop, that's not how I sound.
- Emmet, how was your day today?

- What are you talking
about that is his voice.

- Put some clothes on, our
neighbors are out there.
They can't see any of this.
I get it, I get it.

- Hey, did you put a picture
of me sleeping on Facebook?
- What do you mean who is this?

- I'm afraid you might have
the wrong phone number, sir.

Can you believe we've
been together 12 years?
- Yeah, but we've really only been in love
If you subtract all the times that like

you've been annoying or
I've been mad at you.
- All right, turn it around Nicky Manaj.
